properties.areaDesc: Davis Mountains; Guadalupe Mountains Above 7000 Feet; Eastern Culberson County; Guadalupe and Delaware Mountains; Guadalupe Mountains of Eddy County
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 22 at 3:19AM CST until January 22 at 6:00PM CST by NWS Midland/Odessa TX
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 25 to 40 mph with gusts up to 55 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Guadalupe and Delaware Mountains, Eastern Culberson,
and Davis Mountains.

* WHEN...From 10 AM CST /9 AM MST/ this morning to 6 PM CST /5
PM MST/ this evening.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM CST /9 AM MST/ THIS MORNING TO 6 PM CST /5 PM MST/ THIS EVENING
